						               													<description>In this game you play as Carrot hero who tries to protect its own village from the horde of Rabbits that attack your village. But in reality, Carrot can&amp;rsquo;t win against Rabbit. You don&amp;rsquo;t have any other choice than lure it to others village hope it eat them and get full then leave your village alone after that.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game objective is to be a sole survivor of the game, at the start of the game player will get to choose their hero by randomize. For the start of each turn player will draw invading Rabbit from the deck and place it anywhere on any player&amp;rsquo;s village board. Each Rabbit will have attack direction on their card at the final phase of your turn. Next, the player can draw adventure card(an event type card) which have various effects.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you meet the condition you can use your hero Ultimate attack, then you will enter final phase which Rabbits on your village board will go rampage and do damage to direction their pointed at.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you died in the game you village board will flip to the &amp;ldquo;Village ruin&amp;rdquo;, and you became vengeful spirit, when its comes to your turn again draw one rabbit card and place it on any alive player village board(can&amp;rsquo;t place on any village ruin including your own). Continuing until only last village stands in the game , that is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
